an\nsettlement models based on Sentinel-2 data and deep learning, in both rural and\nurban areas, as compared to earlier, Landsat-based versions of the Global Human\nSettlement Layer.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Mar 2023 22:09:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-03"}
