ts and\nspecifications of both the underlying and overlaying grid level. The results\nshow interdependent concentric flexibility regions or Feasible Operating\nRegions (FORs) in accordance with the manipulation of the weighted objective\nfunction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Mar 2023 09:42:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-03"}
