l step\ntowards bringing together nuclear structure theory, where 3N force is routinely\nused, and nuclear direct reaction theory, based on two-nucleon interactions\nonly.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Mar 2023 11:46:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-22"}
