ve a drop in average model accuracy of more than $45\\%$ and $40\\%$ on\nVGG19 for ImageNet and Resnet34 for Caltech-101, respectively, using only $20$\nraindrops.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Mar 2023 15:14:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-03"}
