derstand computational logic.\nLastly, in addition to understanding computational logic, teachers should also\nfocus on developing students' mathematical thinking quality, enabling students\nto select optimal computational strategies and improve their algorithm\nselection abilities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Mar 2023 08:05:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-06"}
